1. B2B / Flote Auto (/servicii-flote)

    Why you need it: B2C (regular drivers) brings you one car. B2B (local delivery companies, real estate agents, sales teams) brings you 10 to 50 cars.

    The Funnel Play: A page speaking directly to business owners. Keywords: Prioritate la reparații, facturare centralizată, mentenanță preventivă. A business owner's biggest fear is a car sitting idle, losing money. Promise them speed.

